---
title: Cheesy Turkey Potato Casserole with Spinach Salad
description: You start with a meat sauce, top it with crispy potatoes, smother everything in cheese then throw it in the oven for a few minutes and dinner is served! We've got your veggies covered with a spinach salad to go alongside, too!
